detail.name: Warp-sama
detail.effect:
[Activate Main] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck, reveal up to 1 card with <DA> in its card name and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of their owner's deck in a random order.
[Activate Battle][Opponent's Turn] Your cards that are in a battle get +15000 power for the battle.

detail.name: ワープさま
detail.effect:
【起動 メイン】自分のデッキの上から5枚を見て、カード名に「DA」を含むカード1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
【起動 戦闘中】【相手のターン中】自分の戦闘中のカードは、この戦闘中、パワー+15000。
